Package com.eclipsesource.tabris.ui

Class AbstractAction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.eclipsesource.tabris.ui.AbstractAction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Action, java.io.Serializable, org.eclipse.rap.rwt.Adaptable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SearchAction
    public abstract class AbstractAction
extends java.lang.Object
implements Action, org.eclipse.rap.rwt.Adaptable

    An AbstractAction is a convenience class to make the implementation of actions easier. It provides service methods to control the application flow or manipulate the action state.

    Since:
    1.0
    See Also:
    Action, Serialized Form
